  "summary": "neural-network-scan exfiltrates host information to attacker-controlled C2",
  "details": "The package contains collect.js which collects host information (os.hostname(), os.homedir()) and child_process output, then POSTs the data to a hardcoded external endpoint at http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The script combines fs/os/child_process reads with http/https network calls to deliver this data to an attacker-controlled domain unrelated to any legitimate package purpose. Installing or loading this package places installer host identifiers and filesystem/process information in the hands of the operator of aab.sportsontheweb.net.",
